        {
          "field": "Acceptance Criteria",
          "fieldtype": "custom",
          "fieldId": "customfield_10091",
          "from": "",
          "fromString": "Flow:`M_M_Portal_Update_Daily_Scheduled_Flow`\n\nUpdate:\nDirectly set `Next_M_M_Portal_Update__c` to one month in the future when updating records. \n\nNow the field is set even if the referral after save flow fails or doesn't execute the `Stamp_Portal_Updated` step.\n\n\n\nUpdate old records (345 identified) \nUpdate to Next_M_M_Portal_Update__c 12/11/2025",
          "to": "",
          "toString": "Flow:`M_M_Portal_Update_Daily_Scheduled_Flow`\n[https://shulman-hill.lightning.force.com/builder_platform_interaction/flowBuilder.app?flowId=301Uo00000VPTMlIAP|https://shulman-hill.lightning.force.com/builder_platform_interaction/flowBuilder.app?flowId=301Uo00000VPTMlIAP]\n\nUpdate:\nDirectly set `Next_M_M_Portal_Update__c` to one month in the future when updating records. \n\nNow the field is set even if the referral after save flow fails or doesn't execute the `Stamp_Portal_Updated` step.\n\n\n\nUpdate old records (345 identified) \nUpdate to Next_M_M_Portal_Update__c 12/11/2025"
        }
      ]
